          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-060-28D--headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-060-28D--headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-060-28D--headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-060-28D--headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-060-28D--headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-060-28D--headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">P</hi>E<hi rend="small-caps">RUSE</hi> my Leaves thro' ev'ry Part,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-2" n="2">And think thou seest my Owner's Heart,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-3" n="3">Scrawl'd o'er with Trifles thus, and quite</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-4" n="4">As hard, as senseless, and as light;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-5" n="5">Exposed to every Coxcomb's Eyes,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-6" n="6">But hid with Caution from the Wise.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-7" n="7">Here you may read (<hi rend="italics">Dear Charming Saint</hi>)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-8" n="8">Beneath (<hi rend="italics">A new Receipt for Pant</hi>:)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-9" n="9">Here in Beau-spelling (<hi rend="italics">tru tel Deth</hi>,)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-10" n="10">There in her own (<hi rend="italics">far an el breth</hi>.)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-11" n="11">Here (<hi rend="italics">lovely Nymph pronounce my Doom</hi>,)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-12" n="12">There (<hi rend="italics">a safe Way to use Perfume</hi>;)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-13" n="13">Here a Page fill'd with Billet-Doux;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-14" n="14">On t'other Side (<hi rend="italics">laid out for Shoes:)</hi></l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-15" n="15"><hi rend="italics">(Madam, I die without your Grace</hi>,)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-16" n="16">(Item, <hi rend="italics">for half a Yard of Lace</hi>.)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-17" n="17">Who that had Wit would place it here,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-18" n="18">For every peeping Fop to jeer?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-19" n="19">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-20" n="20">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-21" n="21">In Power of Spittle, and a Clout,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-22" n="22">When'er he please to blot it out;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-23" n="23">And then, to heighten the Disgrace,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-24" n="24">Clap his own Nonsense in the Place.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-25" n="25">Whoe'er expects to hold his Part</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-26" n="26">In such a Book and such a Heart,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-27" n="27">If he be wealthy, and a Fool,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-28" n="28">Is in all Points the fittest Tool;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-29" n="29">Of whom it may be justly said,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-28D--line-30" n="30">He's a Golden Pencil tipp'd with Lead.</l>
          </lg>
